[
  {
    "startTime": 13.96,
    "endTime": 16.240000000000002,
    "text": "Words matter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.48,
    "endTime": 21.656,
    "text": "They can heal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.68,
    "endTime": 22.96,
    "text": "and they can kill ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.4,
    "endTime": 26.959999999999997,
    "text": "yet, they have a limit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.96,
    "endTime": 30.96,
    "text": "When I was in eighth grade,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.6,
    "endTime": 36.616,
    "text": "my teacher gave me a vocabulary sheet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.64,
    "endTime": 39.2,
    "text": "with the word \"genocide.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.12,
    "endTime": 45.76,
    "text": "I hated it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.84,
    "endTime": 51.32000000000001,
    "text": "The word genocide is clinical ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.48,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "overgeneral ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.64,
    "endTime": 58.776,
    "text": "bloodless ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.8,
    "endTime": 60.64,
    "text": "dehumanizing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.28,
    "endTime": 64.8,
    "text": "No word"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.24,
    "endTime": 68.416,
    "text": "can describe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.44,
    "endTime": 71.56,
    "text": "what this does to a nation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.16,
    "endTime": 75.896,
    "text": "You need to know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.92,
    "endTime": 77.60000000000001,
    "text": "in this kind of war,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.12,
    "endTime": 81.60000000000001,
    "text": "husbands kills wives,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.64,
    "endTime": 85.8,
    "text": "wives kill husbands,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.6,
    "endTime": 89.96,
    "text": "neighbors and friends kill each other."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.64,
    "endTime": 94.96,
    "text": "Someone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.12,
    "endTime": 97.336,
    "text": "in power"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.36,
    "endTime": 98.56,
    "text": "says,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.96,
    "endTime": 101.16,
    "text": "\"Those over there ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.52,
    "endTime": 103.8,
    "text": "they don't belong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.68,
    "endTime": 106.4,
    "text": "They're not human.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.12,
    "endTime": 109.36,
    "text": "And people believe it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.76,
    "endTime": 114.96000000000001,
    "text": "I don't want words"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.12,
    "endTime": 116.64,
    "text": "to describe this kind of behavior."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.72,
    "endTime": 122.32,
    "text": "I want words to stop it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.8,
    "endTime": 127.48,
    "text": "But where are the words to stop this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.12,
    "endTime": 131.4,
    "text": "And how do we find the words?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.12,
    "endTime": 139.76,
    "text": "But I believe, truly, we have to keep trying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.96,
    "endTime": 144.6,
    "text": "I was born in Kigali, Rwanda."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.12,
    "endTime": 150.24,
    "text": "I felt loved by my entire family"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.24,
    "endTime": 152.60000000000002,
    "text": "and my neighbors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 158.296,
    "text": "I was constantly being teased by everybody,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.32,
    "endTime": 160.92,
    "text": "especially my two older siblings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.24,
    "endTime": 164.20000000000002,
    "text": "When I lost my front tooth,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.44,
    "endTime": 167.536,
    "text": "my brother looked at me and said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.56,
    "endTime": 170.16,
    "text": "\"Oh, it has happened to you, too?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.92,
    "endTime": 173.416,
    "text": "It will never grow back.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.44,
    "endTime": 174.456,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.48,
    "endTime": 176.696,
    "text": "I enjoyed playing everywhere,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.72,
    "endTime": 180.72,
    "text": "especially my mother's garden and my neighbor's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.48,
    "endTime": 183.56,
    "text": "I loved my kindergarten."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.44,
    "endTime": 186.856,
    "text": "We sang songs,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.88,
    "endTime": 188.136,
    "text": "we played everywhere"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.16,
    "endTime": 189.64,
    "text": "and ate lunch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.6,
    "endTime": 194.936,
    "text": "I had a childhood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.96,
    "endTime": 198.68,
    "text": "that I would wish for anyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.68,
    "endTime": 202.4,
    "text": "But when I was six,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.4,
    "endTime": 209.16,
    "text": "the adults in my family began to speak in whispers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.4,
    "endTime": 212.88,
    "text": "and shushed me any time that I asked a question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.0,
    "endTime": 216.256,
    "text": "One night,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.28,
    "endTime": 217.96,
    "text": "my mom and dad came."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.2,
    "endTime": 221.92,
    "text": "They had this strange look when they woke us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.64,
    "endTime": 228.93499999999997,
    "text": "They sent my older sister Claire and I to our grandparent's,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.96,
    "endTime": 231.88,
    "text": "hoping whatever was happening would blow away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.16,
    "endTime": 237.68,
    "text": "Soon we had to escape from there, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.4,
    "endTime": 240.816,
    "text": "We hid,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.84,
    "endTime": 242.56,
    "text": "we crawled,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.8,
    "endTime": 243.36,
    "text": "we sometimes ran."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.84,
    "endTime": 252.84,
    "text": "Sometimes I heard laughter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.88,
    "endTime": 258.399,
    "text": "and then screaming and crying"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.6,
    "endTime": 262.12,
    "text": "and then noise that I had never heard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.0,
    "endTime": 265.216,
    "text": "You see,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.24,
    "endTime": 267.12,
    "text": "I did not know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.4,
    "endTime": 271.67999999999995,
    "text": "what those noises were."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.56,
    "endTime": 274.856,
    "text": "They were neither human --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.88,
    "endTime": 277.36,
    "text": "and also at the same time, they were human."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.68,
    "endTime": 282.48,
    "text": "I saw people who were not breathing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.92,
    "endTime": 285.76,
    "text": "I thought they were asleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.48,
    "endTime": 293.37600000000003,
    "text": "I still didn't understand what death was,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.4,
    "endTime": 295.919,
    "text": "or killing in itself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.76,
    "endTime": 301.256,
    "text": "When we would stop to rest for a little bit"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.28,
    "endTime": 303.215,
    "text": "or search for food,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.24,
    "endTime": 305.176,
    "text": "I would close my eyes,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.2,
    "endTime": 307.736,
    "text": "hoping when I opened them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.76,
    "endTime": 309.159,
    "text": "I would be awake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.48,
    "endTime": 314.84000000000003,
    "text": "I had no idea which direction was home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.8,
    "endTime": 318.76,
    "text": "Days were for hiding"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.12,
    "endTime": 322.4,
    "text": "and night for walking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.28,
    "endTime": 333.296,
    "text": "You go from a person who's away from home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.32,
    "endTime": 335.56,
    "text": "to a person with no home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.2,
    "endTime": 339.856,
    "text": "The place that is supposed to want you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.88,
    "endTime": 341.56,
    "text": "has pushed you out,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.36,
    "endTime": 347.92,
    "text": "and no one takes you in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.76,
    "endTime": 351.12,
    "text": "You are unwanted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.16,
    "endTime": 354.6,
    "text": "by anyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.76,
    "endTime": 359.8,
    "text": "You are a refugee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.24,
    "endTime": 364.456,
    "text": "From age six to 12,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.48,
    "endTime": 366.76,
    "text": "I lived in seven different countries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.56,
    "endTime": 371.76,
    "text": "moving from one refugee camp to another,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.72,
    "endTime": 375.16,
    "text": "hoping we would be wanted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.2,
    "endTime": 380.575,
    "text": "My older sister Claire,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.6,
    "endTime": 382.48,
    "text": "she became a young mother ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.32,
    "endTime": 388.44,
    "text": "and a master at getting things done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.92,
    "endTime": 391.81600000000003,
    "text": "When I was 12,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.84,
    "endTime": 396.56,
    "text": "I came to America with Claire and her family on refugee status."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.96,
    "endTime": 402.616,
    "text": "And that's only the beginning,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.64,
    "endTime": 405.656,
    "text": "because even though I was 12 years old,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.68,
    "endTime": 407.896,
    "text": "sometimes I felt like three years old"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.92,
    "endTime": 409.92,
    "text": "and sometimes 50 years old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.96,
    "endTime": 412.775,
    "text": "My past receded,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.8,
    "endTime": 414.16,
    "text": "grew jumbled,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.4,
    "endTime": 415.23999999999995,
    "text": "distorted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.2,
    "endTime": 419.56,
    "text": "Everything was too much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.8,
    "endTime": 420.44,
    "text": "and nothing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.88,
    "endTime": 428.15999999999997,
    "text": "Time seemed like pages torn out of a book"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.4,
    "endTime": 429.91999999999996,
    "text": "and scattered everywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.6,
    "endTime": 436.40000000000003,
    "text": "This still happens to me standing right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.8,
    "endTime": 442.88,
    "text": "After I got to America,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.84,
    "endTime": 448.88,
    "text": "Claire and I did not talk about our past."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.4,
    "endTime": 453.616,
    "text": "In 2006,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.64,
    "endTime": 455.32,
    "text": "after 12 years"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457.44,
    "endTime": 459.336,
    "text": "being separated away from my family,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.36,
    "endTime": 462.136,
    "text": "and then seven years knowing that they were dead"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 462.16,
    "endTime": 464.0,
    "text": "and them thinking that we were dead,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.88,
    "endTime": 466.68,
    "text": "we reunited ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.48,
    "endTime": 472.96000000000004,
    "text": "in the most dramatic, American way possible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 473.88,
    "endTime": 475.776,
    "text": "Live,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 475.8,
    "endTime": 477.416,
    "text": "on television --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.44,
    "endTime": 478.576,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.6,
    "endTime": 480.16,
    "text": "on \"The Oprah Show.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.4,
    "endTime": 481.856,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.88,
    "endTime": 486.28,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.0,
    "endTime": 490.936,
    "text": "I told you, I told you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.96,
    "endTime": 492.28,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 493.84,
    "endTime": 495.679,
    "text": "But after the show,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.84,
    "endTime": 505.816,
    "text": "as I spent time with my mom and dad"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.84,
    "endTime": 508.496,
    "text": "and my little sister"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.52,
    "endTime": 511.4,
    "text": "and my two new siblings that I never met,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.2,
    "endTime": 515.36,
    "text": "I felt anger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.96,
    "endTime": 521.1600000000001,
    "text": "I felt every deep pain in me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 523.52,
    "endTime": 528.415,
    "text": "And I know that there is absolutely nothing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.44,
    "endTime": 529.6400000000001,
    "text": "nothing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.44,
    "endTime": 535.4960000000001,
    "text": "that could restore the time we lost with each other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.52,
    "endTime": 538.24,
    "text": "and the relationship we could've had."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.48,
    "endTime": 544.6560000000001,
    "text": "Soon, my parents moved to the United States,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.68,
    "endTime": 545.88,
    "text": "but like Claire,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547.2,
    "endTime": 550.72,
    "text": "they don't talk about our past."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.2,
    "endTime": 556.216,
    "text": "They live in never-ending present."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.24,
    "endTime": 559.256,
    "text": "Not asking too many questions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.28,
    "endTime": 562.72,
    "text": "not allowing themselves to feel --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.24,
    "endTime": 567.88,
    "text": "moving in small steps."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.8,
    "endTime": 574.76,
    "text": "None of us, of course, can make sense of what happened to us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.68,
    "endTime": 581.4,
    "text": "Though my family is alive --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.84,
    "endTime": 585.416,
    "text": "yes, we were broken,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.44,
    "endTime": 588.176,
    "text": "and yes, we are numb"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 588.2,
    "endTime": 593.0,
    "text": "and we were silenced by our own experience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 595.8,
    "endTime": 600.319,
    "text": "It's not just my family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602.32,
    "endTime": 607.96,
    "text": "Rwanda is not the only country"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 607.12,
    "endTime": 610.5600000000001,
    "text": "where people have turned on each other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.8,
    "endTime": 611.52,
    "text": "and murdered each other."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.44,
    "endTime": 615.8000000000001,
    "text": "The entire human race,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617.64,
    "endTime": 618.896,
    "text": "in many ways,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.92,
    "endTime": 620.439,
    "text": "is like my family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.8,
    "endTime": 625.496,
    "text": "Not dead;"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.52,
    "endTime": 631.576,
    "text": "yes, broken, numb and silenced by the violence of the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 631.6,
    "endTime": 633.28,
    "text": "that has taken over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.68,
    "endTime": 636.896,
    "text": "You see,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.92,
    "endTime": 641.856,
    "text": "the chaos of the violence continues inside"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.88,
    "endTime": 645.16,
    "text": "in the words we use"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.4,
    "endTime": 649.12,
    "text": "and the stories we create every single day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.48,
    "endTime": 657.96,
    "text": "But also on the labels that we impose on ourselves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 657.12,
    "endTime": 658.48,
    "text": "and each other."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.32,
    "endTime": 666.416,
    "text": "Once we call someone \"other,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666.44,
    "endTime": 667.7760000000001,
    "text": "\"less than,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.8,
    "endTime": 669.55,
    "text": "\"one of them\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 669.8,
    "endTime": 670.4399999999999,
    "text": "or \"better than,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.6,
    "endTime": 672.84,
    "text": "believe me ..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 676.8,
    "endTime": 678.8,
    "text": "under the right condition,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.16,
    "endTime": 684.56,
    "text": "it's a short path to more destruction."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.88,
    "endTime": 687.696,
    "text": "More chaos"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 687.72,
    "endTime": 689.5600000000001,
    "text": "and more noise"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 689.8,
    "endTime": 691.28,
    "text": "that we will not understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.8,
    "endTime": 696.12,
    "text": "Words will never be enough"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 697.48,
    "endTime": 702.816,
    "text": "to quantify and qualify the many magnitudes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 702.84,
    "endTime": 705.84,
    "text": "of human-caused destruction."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709.52,
    "endTime": 711.84,
    "text": "In order for us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 713.4,
    "endTime": 717.24,
    "text": "to stop the violence that goes on in the world,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 719.6,
    "endTime": 721.336,
    "text": "I hope --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.36,
    "endTime": 723.896,
    "text": "at least I beg you --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.92,
    "endTime": 725.199,
    "text": "to pause."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 726.96,
    "endTime": 729.0,
